    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨在德国州选举中再次败给极右翼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/scholz-escapes-another-defeat-to-far-right-in-german-state-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的社会民主党击败了极右翼的德国选择党，看上去将在东部勃兰登堡州继续执政，从而使总理和他的政党避免再次遭遇令人尴尬的选举挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/scholz-escapes-another-defeat-to-far-right-in-german-state-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 20:08:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯本周将补充其经济提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/harris-to-unveil-economic-policy-plans-this-week-reuters-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，随着 2024 年总统竞选进入最后六周，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯本周将在她的经济政策议程中添加新的提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/harris-to-unveil-economic-policy-plans-this-week-reuters-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 19:19:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国总理关注企业税，警告债务状况“严重”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-eyes-business-taxes-warns-debt-in-grave-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总理米歇尔·巴尼耶表示，新政府可能会增加大企业和富人的税收，以修复失控的预算赤字并保持债券市场的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/french-premier-eyes-business-taxes-warns-debt-in-grave-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 18:44:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默在失误后努力恢复“变革”叙事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/starmer-struggles-to-reclaim-change-narrative-after-missteps</link>
      <description><![CDATA[基尔·斯塔默希望工党年度大会能够阐明如何向英国选民兑现“变革”承诺。然而，首相及其高级助手们却在第一天试图平息内部对执政头几周所做决定的怀疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/starmer-struggles-to-reclaim-change-narrative-after-missteps</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 18:41:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷或实施限电措施应对夏季用电需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/argentina-would-implement-power-cuts-to-cope-with-summer-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于天气预报显示南半球今年夏季气温将升高，消费者将不得不打开空调，阿根廷计划采取计划性断电措施来应对电力需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/argentina-would-implement-power-cuts-to-cope-with-summer-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 18:39:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨领导的政党在德国州选举中领先于极右翼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/scholz-s-spd-leads-in-brandenburg-state-vote-ahead-of-far-right</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的社会民主党似乎抵挡住了极右翼德国选择党的强劲挑战，保住了东部勃兰登堡地区的权力，使总理和他的政党避免再次遭遇令人尴尬的选举挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/scholz-s-spd-leads-in-brandenburg-state-vote-ahead-of-far-right</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 16:07:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反对者提出谴责议案，法国政府面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/france-s-government-is-at-risk-as-opponents-eye-a-censure-motion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的新政府立即引起各政治派别的愤怒反应，增加了政府迅速垮台的风险，这将进一步给法国紧张的公共财政前景蒙上阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/france-s-government-is-at-risk-as-opponents-eye-a-censure-motion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 10:52:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉巴马州警方称伯明翰深夜枪击事件造成四人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/4-killed-in-late-night-shooting-in-birmingham-alabama-police-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉巴马州伯明翰（美联社）周六，在阿拉巴马州伯明翰一处受欢迎的夜生活场所，多名枪手开枪射击，造成 4 人死亡，17 人受伤，警方称这是针对其中一名被杀害者进行的有针对性的“射击”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/4-killed-in-late-night-shooting-in-birmingham-alabama-police-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 07:25:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
